metadata.name: Pink Lady #1
metadata.description:
# The Pink Ladies

The Pink Ladies are an elite unit of the Deltanauts, dedicated to empowerment and equality all across the metaverse. 

Led by their fearless leaders, BossGirls. BossGirls and the Pink Ladies use their intelligence, tenacity, and teamwork to step into foreign territory, breaking down walls, giving a voice and power to the voiceless, by building a better future for all Deltians. BossGirls and the Pink Ladies are a force that sees the importance of building and fighting for equity and fairness, early in our collective exploration of the metaverse. The challenges that exist in the realverse are not forgotten. 

While many spaces are not equal for all yet, the passion, bravery, and determination of the Pink Ladies will be unrelenting until the mission is accomplished, in both the metaverse and the realverse. 

**Ad Astra Ladies!**

Created by [DeltaFlare](https://deltaflare.gg)
